# Description
# -----------
# Deploys MSIMPL microservices inside the Docker environment.
#
# Prerequisites
# -------------
# • Docker Infrastructure (Kafka, Kafka UI) must already be running.
# • PostgreSQL runs on Windows Host.
# • All containers communicate through infra_msimpl-network.
# • Kafka Endpoint : kafka:9092
# • PostgreSQL     : host.docker.internal
#
# Startup Sequence
# ----------------
# Infrastructure
#      ↓
# Config Server
#      ↓
# Discovery Server
#      ↓
# Authentication Server
#      ↓
# API Gateway
#      ↓
# Business Microservices
#
# =============================================================================

